						               													<description>Welcome to the world of Questicus, a hand-drawn adventure of epic questing and fierce competition for up to 3 to 6 players. The idea is simple: become the most influential adventurer in a given time to become the next Mayor of the Town and win the game. Your worst enemy is your fellow players as they are also fighting for power and influence. Utilize an arsenal of magical items, cunning skills, and secretive plots to become the reigning Mayor over the land!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Enjoy an engaging adventure as players create the map as they explore the world around them. With 38 unique tiles and over 50 special events, you&amp;rsquo;ll never play the same game twice! Every time you start a game you will be thrown into a brand new experience with new challenges and different strategies for you to apply. Vie for power and influence with one of twelve exciting characters! Will you choose to be a good adventurer seeking to help the people, or an evildoer who seeks to destroy all those that stand in their way? In Questicus the choice is yours with each character having their very own stats and abilities specific to them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Worried a game might drag on too long? Afraid that the game will be over to soon? Well fear not, Questicus has just the thing for you! With Questicus, we set up a way to keep track of how many rounds are left in a game by using &amp;ldquo;Town Event&amp;rdquo; cards. Each round, one of these cards will be drawn and revealed with a special event that all players participate in. Customize your experience with a simple game of 10 rounds, or go in for the long haul and set up a 35 round game! The choice is up to you, as we know players like games tailored to their needs and with Questicus you are given the freedom to choose the length of the game you want to play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Are you ready to get questing?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
